Aledari Heavy Weapons Technical Analysis

Or, should you use anything else other than Bright Lances in 10th ed?

Author

The Stat Seer

Published

March 1, 2025

Intro

Aeldari heavy weapons are a set of 5 weapons that have been part of many Aeldari (or Eldar way before) since 3rd edition. They’ve been part of some of the most iconic model kits of the faction.

Weapons

War Walkers, Wraithlord, Falcons, Wave Serpents and Guardians Defenders all can choose one or more of the following weaponry:

- WEAPON RANGE A BS S AP D
Missile launcher – starshot
48” 1 3+ 10 -2 D6
Missile launcher – sunburst [Blast]
48” D6 3+ 4 -1 1
Bright lance
36” 1 3+ 12 -3 D6+2
Scatter laser [Sustained Hits 1]
36” 6 3+ 5 0 1
Shuriken cannon [Lethal Hits]
24” 3 3+ 6 -1 2
Starcannon
36” 2 3+ 8 -3 2
